<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" ng-app="myApp">

<head>
    <base href="/">
    
    <!--Site CSS-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/stylesheets/css/main.css">
    <title>Richie Tarkowski | Software Developer</title>

    <% include ../partials/header %>
</head>

<body>
    <nav>   
        <% include ../partials/navbar %>

        <div id="nav-personal">
            <p>
                <div id="name" ng-controller="personalInfo"> RICHIE TARKOWSKI </div>
            </p>
        </div>
        <div id="nav-title">
            &mdash; <span id = "full-degree">Computer Information Systems</span><span id = "abbr-degree">CIS</span> Major at FSU &mdash;
        </div>
        <div id = "read-more">
            <a href = "#about-me"><button class = "styled-btn">CONTINUE</button></a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main>
        <section class="about-me" id = "about-me">
            <div id="links-head">&mdash; About Me &mdash;</div>
            <div id="intro">
                <div id="info">
                    <div>My name is Richie Tarkowski, and I am a Computer Information Systems student at Northwestern Michigan College and Ferris State University. I currently work part-time at Hagerty as an IT Applications Intern. Post-education, my goal is to apply my knowledge of software engineering to design and develop applications. I have experience in building .NET applications with C# and WPF, creating SQL/MySQL databases and performing DML/DDL statements, using Git and GitHub for version control, developing responsive and mobile websites, and writing server-side scripts. Additionally, I have automated test cases with Selenium Web-Driver, Java, and JavaScript frameworks. In my free time, I enjoy reading, exercising, investing, and learning about technologies that are not covered in my CIS classes.</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="resume">
                <a href="../../static/media/Tarkowski_Resume.pdf" target="_blank"><button id = "resume-download" class = "styled-btn">View My Resume</button></a>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="container" id = "links-top">
            <div id="links-head">&mdash; Connect &mdash;</div>
            <section class="card" ng-controller="links">
                <div class = "card-image" id = "card-github">
                    <a target="_blank" href="{{gitHub.domain}}"><div class = "hover-effect">
                        <span>&mdash; GitHub &mdash;</span>
                    </div></a>
                </div>

                <div class="card-desc">
                    <p>CIS is more than just my major, it's a personal interest. I enjoy applying what I've learned to my own projects. Visit my GitHub to see these applications!</p>
                </div>

                <div class = "card-button">
                    <a target="_blank" href="{{gitHub.domain}}"> <button class="card-link">GitHub <i class="fa fa-angle-double-right"></i></button></a>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="card" ng-controller="links">
                <div class = "card-image" id = "card-trailhead">
                    <a target="_blank" href="{{trailHead}}"> <div class = "hover-effect">
                        <span>&mdash; Trailhead &mdash;</span>
                    </div> </a>
                </div>
                
                <div class="card-desc">
                    <p>Track my progress in Salesforce Trailhead to see what I'm learning about. Also, checkout my <a target = "_blank" href = "https://trailhead.salesforce.com/users/0055000000875A3AAI/trailmixes/developer-trailmix">Developer Trailmix</a>, a combination of all of my favorite trailheads.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="card-button">
                    <a target="_blank" href="{{trailHead}}"> <button class="card-link">Trailhead <i class="fa fa-angle-double-right"></i></button> </a>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="card" ng-controller="links">
                <div class = "card-image" id = "card-linkedin">
                    <a target="_blank" href="{{linkedIn}}"> <div class = "hover-effect">
                        <span>&mdash; LinkedIn &mdash;</span>
                    </div> </a>
                </div>

                <div class="card-desc">
                    <p>Want to get to know me more? Let's get in touch! Send me a message on LinkedIn or take a look at my profile to learn about other activities that I've participated in.</p>
                </div>

                <div class = "card-button">
                    <a target="_blank" href="{{linkedIn}}"> <button class="card-link">LinkedIn <i class="fa fa-angle-double-right"></i></button> </a>
                </div>
            </section>
        </section>

        <section class="projects" id = "projects-top" ng-controller="projects">
            <div id="projects-header">&mdash; Projects &mdash;</div>
            <div id="filter" class="disabled">
                <select ng-model = "selected_type"  ng-change="ProjectFilter()">
                    <option ng-repeat="type in types" value="{{ type.value }}">{{type.label}}</option>
                </select>
            </div>
            <div class="proj" id = "hagerty" data-tags="js,sql,node">
                <div class="proj-head off-black">
                    Test Automation
                </div>
                <hr><br>
                <div class="proj-desc">
                    <span>Overview:</span> Responsible for designing, building, and managing a test automation application at Hagerty to ensure that Salesforce apps and web processes were fully functional in multiple environments. <br><br>
                    <span>Technologies Used:</span> NightwatchJS, Typescript, SQL, NodeJS
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="proj, disabled" data-tags="c#">
                <div class="proj-head off-black">
                    Despair
                </div>
                <hr><br>
                <div class="proj-desc" ng-controller="links">
                    <span>Overview:</span> Developed a Text-Based Quest Game using programming concepts
                    such as: Polymorphism, Inheritance, Encapsulation, Interfaces, and Events. This application adheres to the MVC Design Pattern and the Dependicy Injection Principle.
                    <br><br>
                    <span>Technologies Used:</span> C# <br><br>
                    <span class = "last-updated">Last Updated:</span> <label id = "cit195-date"> </label>
                    <br><br>
                    <a target="_blank" href="{{gitHub.domain + gitHub.cit195}}">GitHub</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="proj" data-tags="php,sql,html/css">
                <div class="proj-head off-black">
                    March Madness Discussion Forum
                </div>
                <hr><br>
                <div class="proj-desc" ng-controller="links">
                    <span>Overview:</span> Created a Discussion Forum web application that features user authentication and the ability to add, edit, delete, view, and like posts. <br><br>
                    <span>Technologies Used:</span> PHP, SQL, HTML5, CSS <br><br>
                    <span class = "last-updated">Last Updated:</span> <label id = "cit228-date"> </label>
                    <br><br>
                    <a target="_blank" href="{{gitHub.domain + gitHub.cit190}}">GitHub</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="proj" data-tags="wpf,mongodb,api,c#">
                <div class="proj-head off-black">
                    Stock Insight
                </div>
                <hr><br>
                <div class="proj-desc" ng-controller="links">
                    <span>Overview:</span> Developed a simple, responsive WPF stock application that includes persistence and real-time stock data. <br><br>
                    <span>Technologies Used:</span> Windows Presentation Foundation (WPF), C#, MongoDB, Web API <br><br>
                    <span class = "last-updated">Last Updated:</span> <label id = "cit255-date"> </label>
                    <br><br>
                    <a target="_blank" href="{{gitHub.domain + gitHub.cit255}}">GitHub</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="proj" data-tags="angular,node">
                <div class="proj-head off-black">
                    Chatversity
                </div>
                <hr><br>
                <div class="proj-desc" ng-controller="links">
                    <span>Overview:</span> Designed and built an Angular 7 messaging app with a team. The product features user authentication, messaging, adding connections, user online status, and join/leave/delete room. We also created a static website to promote and support the web app. <a target="_blank" href="https://chatversityapp.com">Visit the static site.</a> <br><br>
                    <span>Technologies Used:</span> Angular 7, NodeJS <br><br>
                    <a target="_blank" href="https://www.chatversity.app">Visit the Web App!</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="proj" data-tags="html/css,js,node">
                <div class="proj-head off-black">
                    E-Portfolio Website
                </div>
                <hr><br>
                <div class="proj-desc" ng-controller="links">
                    <span>Overview:</span> Built this website from scratch using several web technologies. <br><br>
                    <span>Technologies Used:</span> HTML5, CSS, JavaScript, AngularJS, NodeJS <br><br>
                    <span class = "last-updated">Last Updated:</span> <label id = "eportfolio-date"> </label>
                    <br><br>
                    <a target="_blank" href="{{gitHub.domain + gitHub.eportfolio}}">GitHub</a>
                </div>
            </div>
